 A finely designed dashboard sits upfront, integrated with all the functions of the vehicle. Cool wood inserts form the dashboard and door panels, making for a far more luxurious feel within the cabin. The stylized, three spoke steering wheel is incorporated with various control and convenience functions for the best aid of the driver. Chrome finished bull-eye shaped AC vents bring the best blend of form and function. A chrome finished gear lever takes the ride and driving experience to an edge in terms of luxury. A center console storage illumination, tread plates inscribed with the company's name, and foot pedals with the letter 'B' branded in them together make for a refined environment for the occupants.Interior Comfort:Comfort is a very great necessity for the vehicles of the day, and this car ensures that nothing is left behind in terms of the quality of its interiors. It has a windscreen designed to sense rain and to automatically activate its wipers. It has an electronic tyre pressure monitoring system that brings all the best aid to the driver, ensuring that safety and comfort are welded in one. The ride offers suspension settings through its HD screen, and the tyre pressure as well, matching comfort with safety as well. A multi-zone automatic climate control function keeps the cabin environment fresh and ambient. Other notable features include a park distance control display function, a remote garage door opening and an electronic parking brake function among others. The ride experience is refined with the aid of an electronic cruise function.Interior Measurements:A massive interior cabin provides more than enough room for a small family. Ample room is available to house large, lanky and broad shouldered men, along with those with tall physiques and long legs. The seats are large and well cushioned, ensuring that the best quality is also offered to the passengers. A massive trunk space of 358 litres is provided for the utmost needs of its owners.Powered by the W12 plant, the vehicle can touch a top speed of 331kmph, which makes it among the fastest machines built. In addition to this, this mill also propels the machine to the 100kmph mark within just 4.2 seconds. Coming to the V8 mill, the top speed under this engine is 309kmph, while the peak acceleration is equally good at 4.5 seconds.As mentioned earlier, of the eight versions, four are equipped with a V8 drive-train that has a displacement value of 3993cc, while the other four have a W12 mill that gives a displacement capacity of 5998cc. Starting with the V8 mill, it is a 4.0-litre drive-train that consists of eight cylinders incorporated together. Furthermore, has a twin turbocharged mechanism, giving enhanced performance. It produces a max power of 521bhp along with a torque of 680Nm. The other four members of the series are armed with a 6.0-litre W12 mill, which consists of 12 cylinders put together. A twin turbocharger is present for this mill as well, giving better speed capacity to those variants. It churns out 626bhp of superior power along with 820Nm of mammoth torque. All of the power-plants are mated to a ZF 8-speed automatic transmission gear box, which ensures smoother shifting capacity.For the W12 plant, the peak mileage among all of the variants is a strong 10.3kmpl. Coming to the other engine variant, which is the eight cylinder V8 train, this mill manages a mileage value of 9.4kmpl which is also quite good considering its segment.Coming to the specifications, the eight cylinder V8 mill displace 3993cc. Coming to the other values, it produces a peak torque of 680Nm, along with a max power of 521bhp. The machine is also available with a 12 cylinder W12 power-plant, which has a displacement of 5998cc. It also renders a peak torque of 820Nm, along with a power of 626bhp.This vehicle is equipped with an advanced Infotainment system, gifted with a high resolution 8-inch touchscreen display. This goes in integration with several other cool features. It has a radio feature, a DVD slot and a USB insertion slot as well. An advanced HVAC control system is also incorporated here. Advanced, mode radiator speakers arm the cabin for the best musical experience. They are enhanced with the combined function of separate tweeters and mid range speakers, for a high quality audio expensive. A Bluetooth facility is also present, giving the luxury of audio streaming and in-cabin call hosting. The cabin also includes volumetric ultrasonic alarm, a satellite radio, and a unique GPS tracking system. The ride experience and ease of driving are refined with the aid of an electronic cruise function. Sealing it all off, the vehicle has a function for parking distance control, and a remote garage door opening as well.The high grade speed benefits that this vehicle offers is cemented with control and ride stability. It has advanced braking calipers fitted on both front and rear wheels, ensuring that the braking performance meets the needs of the ride. Furthermore, carbon ceramic brakes are available as additional features, enhancing the braking ability even further. Going beyond conventions known to automobiles, this vehicle hits the technological frontier to advance its control management. It has an anti-lock braking system, along with electronic brake force distribution. The function of handling that the vehicle's technologies offer are further refined with a hydraulic brake assistance function. Sealing the list of high tech control aids, the vehicle is gifted with an electronic stability program, an aquaplane detection function that ensures the firmest safety on wet grounds, and a drag torque control system. Its suspension system is just as high grade as its braking, ensuring that the vehicle is guarded with balance and stability at all levels. A computer controlled self leveling air suspension system, with anti-roll bars, bring the firmest suspension standards to the car. In addition to this, the front axle has a four link double wishbone, while the rear one is equipped with a mutli link system for the very best ride stability. Both the axles are gifted with air springs that have continuous damping control, keeping the ride smooth by absorbing all bumps and jerks along the way. A speed sensitive power assisted steering system further raises control.This vehicle is secured with the presence of a reliable array of safety features. Tight seatbelts strap the passengers in, while airbags provide a cushioned protection from all sides. A knee airbag also exists for the driver, keeping track of all needs in case of an emergency. The anti-lock braking system and brake force distribution enforce a good ride stability The advanced stability control feature is programmed to keep a trace on the vehicle's control, sensing if its handling limits have been exceeded and pulling the engine power down in a case where they have. In addition to this, its powerful, high beam bi-xenon headlights give the vehicle a far greater visibility, ensuring that mishaps are prevented beforehand. An advanced security system armed with theft deterrent alarm function ensures that the security of the car is also highlighted. The engine is disabled with an ignition disable device in a case where the correct key is not used.A set of 21 inch speed alloy wheels, colored in a dark tint finish, are presented as standard wheels for some trims, but additional options exist. In some of the versions, a set of 20 inch, 6 Tri-Spoke design alloy wheels are presented as standard wheels, while the 21 inch alloy wheels available as optional additions.1. Great performance capacity.2. Stunning exterior appearance.3. Great comfort and luxury features inside the car.4. A controlled drive is ensured with the best handling.5. It has a great multimedia system with loads of other accessories. 1. A weak fuel economy and lower mileage.2. Its outer profile leaves its inner space comfort suffering.3. It has a low ground clearance.4. Could use additional safety 