int inertia-reel belts for all seats along with belt tensioners and force limiters at front. The driver and passengers seat belt reminder notification displayed on the instrument panel in the form of acoustic and visual signal.A set of 17-inch cast aluminum wheels enhances the look of its side profile, that are further covered with tubeless radial tyres of size 245/45 R17. These radials are designed to provide exceptional grip on all roads besides ensuring a high level of security and stability as well. It is also offered with a set of 18-inch aluminum wheels, which are available in both 5-arm and 7-arm dynamic design. The firm has covered them with 245/40 R18 sized tubeless radial tyres, which also deliver an impressive performance.1. Acceleration and pickup are reliable. 2. Internal cabin is spacious. 3. Itgives a comfortable driving experience. 4. Appealing with a lot of styling aspects. 5. Safety quotient is quite high.1. Price is not very competitive. 2. Ground clearance is quite low. 3. Head space should be further increased. 4. Interior design can be improvised. 5. Less number of authorized service stations.
