VLamborghini Huracan\u000a is a highly acclaimed super car in the Indian automobile market, which is produced by Italian car manufacturer, Automobili Lamborghini S. p. A. The iconic automaker has launched this vehicle as a replacement for its successful model, Gallardo. Firstly, the car had made its global debut at the 2014 Geneva Auto Expo and now it available in the country car market to enthrall the sports car lovers here. It is being sold with a 5.2-litre, V10 petrol mill under the hood, which comes with a displacement capacity of 5204cc. This engine has the ability of churning out a whopping power of 602bhp in combination with a mammoth torque output of 560Nm, which is quite interesting for Indian road conditions. This petrol motor is coupled with a seven speed LDF dual clutch automatic transmission gear box that delivers a power packed performance. The company has given it a hydraulic dual circuit braking mechanism, which also has vacuum brake servo unit for augmenting its braking mechanism. Its has a hybrid aluminum and carbon fiber chassis, which is lightweight that eventually contributes towards enhancing its safety along with acceleration. On the other hand, it is bestowed with three different drive select modes including Strada, Sport and Corsa, which changes the mechanism of different components of this vehicle to suit the selected drive mode. This super car is all about breathtaking performance and stylishness like no other vehicle in its class. It is blessed with an aerodynamic body structure that is much similar to its sibling, Aventador. It is designed with an angular headlight cluster that is incorporated with high intensity lamps. The wide bumper comes with massive air intake section and it has an ultra modern tail light cluster, which gives the rear end an attractive look. Its neatly crafted wheel arches are bestowed with a set of 5-twin spoke designed alloy wheels with company insignia embedded on it.On the other hand, we can say that this amazing super car is not just classy from outside, but it gets well furnished internal cabin, which gives it a lavish appeal. Its insides look much more spacious and well organized, thanks to the wider instrument cluster and ergonomically positioned toggle switches, which are easy to reach of the driver. The main highlight of this vehicle is its powerful engine sound, which is pretty fearsome and certainly raises your pulse. At the same time, it gets fully LED lighting system both inside and out, which represents the new age of technology. The car maker has given utmost importance to its suspension mechanism incorporating magnetorhetologic system, which is a damper filled with fluid and is controlled by electromagnetic fields. This enables the vehicle to perform exceptionally well irrespective of the road conditions. The cabin is also integrated with signature Dynamic Steering accompanied by bigger shift paddles that makes it quite convenient to glide through traffic. This super car has a low ground clearance that measures just about 135mm, but it can be increased up to 175mm, which helps to deal with speed barriers and uneven road conditions. At present, it will not have any competitor in its segment as its price range is quite higher than any other vehicle with such technical specifications.This luxurious super car has an all new body structure that is made up with an extensive use of carbon fiber and hybrid aluminum, which resulted in excellent built quality. Its aerodynamic body is fitted with several trademark cosmetics, which gives it a new age style on the roads and attracts the car enthusiasts. To begin with the front facade, it has a slanting forward design all the way from windscreen to the front bumper. Its large bonnet is quite attractive and embossed with a prominent company insignia at the tip. The headlight cluster is placed on top of the hood that are angular. It is powered by two projector headlamps and side turn indicator. It also has LED day time running lights as well. Its large front bumper has bigger air intake vents with perforated mesh that contributes towards cooling the engine quickly. Its side profile looks extremely sleek as its overall height measures just about 1165mm. The car maker has has placed the turn indicators on the front wheel arches, which are also visible from front facade. This well molded wheel arches are fitted with a set of 5-twin spoke design alloy wheels that are further covered with high performance Pirelli tubeless radial tyres. Its external wing mirrors are sleekly structured and are done up in dual tone color scheme. Its rear wheel arches are accompanied by an small air vent that allows better air intake for engine. This super car has a futuristic rear profile with wide stance and designed with sleek taillight cluster that is incorporated with high intensity LED brake lamps. The eye catching bumper is painted in body color. Its engine console is covered with a distinctly designed glass with black shade that adds to its next generation appeal. Its rear bumper is in black color and it is equipped with four round shaped exhaust pipes. Furthermore, there is a perforated grille placed just below the taillight cluster that gives it a true super car look. The overall look of this vehicle is complimented by the company insignia that is embedded just above the rear grille.Exterior Measurements:This sports car is designed with a large wheel base of 2620mm, which offers a spacious cabin inside. At the same time, it has an overall length of 4459mm along with a standard height of 1165mm. Its total width is about 1924mm, which includes external rear view mirrors of both sides. This super car has a low ground clearance that measures just about 135mm, but it can be increased up to 175mm, which helps to deal with speed barriers and uneven road conditions.The car manufacturer has given this super car a classy internal cabin that are incorporated with a lot of sophisticated aspects for convenience of its occupants. In terms of seating, it is incorporated with ergonomically designed seats, which are well cushioned and provide sufficient leg space for both driver and the front co-passenger. These are covered with superior quality 'Nappa' leather upholstery that adds to the classy appeal. The seats are integrated with standard backrest with longitudinal adjustment function. Apart from these, for the comfort of its occupants, it also has full electric control for height, tilting along with length adjustment and seat heating facility. The electrically adjustable head restraints are embossed with company badging. The company has covered the lower dashboard, seat center, roof lining and door panel with premium quality leather, which adds to its classiness and gives a luxurious feel, while traveling. The design of its cockpit is based on the "form follows function" principle wherein, the main display is integrated in the instrument cluster and includes center console with a mobile phone holder below. One of the highlights in this vehicle is an advanced company's infotainment system II (LIS II), which includes an advanced music interface system and enhances the ambiance of its cabin. This feature will be very useful to the driver, as it can help them in real time to reach their destination easily. The leather wrapped steering wheel is mounted with multi functional switches, which further adds to the driver's convenience.Interior Comfort:For giving the occupants a pleasurable driving experience, the company has blessed this super car with a lot of sophisticated features. It is incorporated with an advanced air conditioning unit with dual zone control for driver and co-passenger that helps in cooling the cabin quickly. The sophisticated music system is equipped with a number of functions that enhance the ambiance of its entire cabin. It also has a USB interface, i-Pod connectivity, CD charger and RVC kit along with several speakers, which enhances the ambiance of its cabin. Its instrument panel has 12.3 inch TFT touchscreen, which houses various warning lamps and notifications for keeping the driver updated. It also supports satellite navigation system for easy access and Bluetooth connectivity for pairing the mobile phones. This vehicle also has an efficient parking assist along with rear view camera for assisting the driver to park the vehicle safely. It has a leather wrapped multifunctional steering wheel, which is mounted with dynamic mode selector for convenience. Through this, the driver can select from three driving modes that are STARDA, SPORT and CORSA. Being a luxury vehicle, it is fitted with a number of advanced aspects that increases the level of luxury and lavishness of occupants even on the top speed. Apart from all these features, it will also help in changing the setup of main systems in the car including engine and gear box response, suspension stiffness, engine sound, steering and all wheel drive torque distribution. All the features of high usability have been placed within close proximity to the driver.Interior Measurements:The internal cabin of this car is quite roomy, but seating space is available only for two passengers. Although, its overall height is below 1.2 meters. The headroom is quite good owing to its ergonomically designed seats. At the same time, there is a huge leg and shoulder space available in the cockpit that contributes towards ultimate driving comfort. The company has given it a large fuel tank, which can store about 118 litres of petrol in it.The car maker claims that this super car can reach a maximum speed of 325 Kmph, which is rather astounding. Its 5.2-litre engine is mated with a 7-speed LDF dual clutch transmission gear box that enables the vehicle to breach the 100 Kmph mark in just 3.2 seconds that is thrilling for the passengers sitting inside. Furthermore, it can break the 200 Kmph speed barrier from a standstill in mere 9.9 seconds, which is unbelievable.This new model series is equipped with a naturally aspirated 5.2-litre IDS engine under the bonnet that has water and oil cooling system. It comprises of ten cylinders along with a total of forty valves and has the displacement capacity of 5204cc. This machine has Bosch MED 17 Master Slave engine management system and it complies with EURO 6 emission norms. This engine has the capacity of churning out a maximum power of 602bhp at 8250rpm and generates a mammoth torque output of 560Nm at just 6250rpm, which is simply incredible. The car maker has done some minor tweaks to this motor and has improved its CO2 emission to 290 gram per kilometer, which is quite good for a V10 mill. This motor is mated with a seven speed LDF dual clutch automatic transmission gear box that collaborates with drive select modes to distribute torque output to all its four wheels.This super car is powered by a massive ten cylinder based petrol engine that has dry sump lubrification technology, which helps in delivering an incredible performance. It can produce a minimum mileage of 5.61 Kmpl in urbane conditions, which goes up to a maximum of 10.63 Kmpl on the bigger roads, which is quite decent considering the caliber of this vehicle.Under the bonnet, this sports car is fitted with a 5204cc petrol mill that has the ability to produce a commanding power output of 602bhp at 8250rpm. At the same time it delivers a pounding torque output of 560Nm at just 6250rpm, which is quite good for this class.This vehicle is blessed with an advanced Lamborghini Infotainment System II, which is a key aspect of this car. It comes with a optional navigation system, which also have a high quality map display that provides clear 3D views of the area the car is traveling in. There is also a Bluetooth kit available in conjunction with this navigation kit. The occupants can easily make hands free calls through Bluetooth, which adds to their convenience. Its music interface system along with a six CD changer kit which further adds to the entertainment quotient. It also has a lot of speakers along with tweeters, which enhances the the ambiance of the cabin. This stunning car can be customized by its owners with a few more interesting aspects based on their requirement. These include a battery maintainer that preserves the battery by preventing it from discharge by lights and anti theft system as well. It has a digital pressure gauge that helps in keeping the pressure of its tyres under constant control. Another aspect is the rechargeable torch that can be charged conveniently from the 12V power outlet. Apart from these, the owners can add a few more features like a carbon forged rim badge kit, car care kit, racing exhaust as well as satellite anti theft system.The company has given this vehicle an efficient braking as well as suspension mechanism, which keeps it well balanced and stable. This super car has a hybrid aluminum body frame, while its outer skin is made of aluminum and composite material. It is blessed with a hydraulic dual circuit braking mechanism, which also has vacuum brake servo unit, which further augments its braking mechanism. The front wheels are equipped with six piston calipers, whereas the rear wheels are assembled with four piston calipers. On the other hand, the suspension mechanism is quite proficient, which keeps the vehicle rigid at all times. The front and rear axles are fitted with an aluminum double wishbone type of system, which is further accompanied by anti roll bars. The company has blessed it with an electromechanical power steering system along with LDS (Lamborghini Dynamic Steering) and variable ratio. It gives a comfortable driving experience in every conditions.This scintillating Lamborghini Huracan is bestowed with a lot of safety aspects that will ensure protection not only to its occupants but to the vehicle as well and gives a stress free driving experience. It includes a rear view camera along with front and reverse parking sensors, which are helpful, while parking the vehicle. The engine immobilization device functions by avoiding the chances of any unauthorized entry and protects it from theft. The presence of electronic stability control helps in preventing the crashes by minimizing the possibilities of skidding or losing control. This sports car is bestowed with an advanced anti lock braking system that avoids wheel locking. It also prevents the vehicle from skidding during application of sudden brakes and keeps it under the control of its driver. Besides these, the traction control system optimizes its grip and stability especially on slippery surfaces. It is loaded with full size dual stage front as well as lateral airbags that enhances security to its passengers in case of collision. Moreover, it has low tyre pressure warning light, which alerts the driver when its tyre pressure is low or going flat. In addition to these, it includes side impact beams, security system, outboard front lap and shoulder safety belts as well as airbag passenger switch, which adds to the safety quotient. On the other hand, the buyers can further customize it with satellite anti-theft system. This comes with a secure and reliable tracking system that avoids the engine to start in case of theft. All these features put together makes it one of the safest vehicle in its class.The front wheel arches are equipped with a stylish set of 8.5J x 20 inch alloy wheels that have been fitted with 'Pirelli' 245/30 R20 sized tubeless tyres. Whereas the rear arches are fitted with a pair of 11J x 20 inch alloy wheels that are covered with 305/30 R20 sized radial tyres. These provide not only superior grip on roads but also deliver excellent performance.1. Sophisticated external appearance with a lot of styling aspects. 2. Breathtaking engine performance along with decent acceleration and pickup. 3. Innovative Magnetorhetologic suspension adds to the driving comfort. 4. Hybrid aluminum and carbon fiber body construction is its big plus point. 5. High end safety standards adds to its advantage.1. Its availability as a CBU unit adds to its disadvantage. 2. Cost of maintenance and spares is highly expensive. 3. Most of the comfort features are available as optional. 4. Low ground clearance can be problematic. 5. Price tag is quite expensive.
